<br>
One person bashing a mob wont interupt many spells, 2 people bashing a mob will interupt a lot of spells, 3 people will stop it casting almost completely.<br>
<br>
Was an lovely thing you could do when hunting Sebilis, i remember a shadowkight friend i had on another server, together we could keep things from never casting a single spell.. was really amusing sometimes when fighting the shaman/wizarsd frogloks.<br>
